#. module: software_reseller
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:software_reseller.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Licenses App</font></strong>, specially tailored for the Software reseller industry, you can have an overview of all your software licenses. Click on one specific license to track license\n"
"            keys belonging to each customer."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບໃບອະນຸຍາດ</font></strong>, ທີ່ຖືກອອ"
"ກແບບມາສະເພາະສຳລັບທຸລະກິດຂາຍຊອບແວຄືນ, ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງໃບອະນຸຍາດທັງໝົດໄດ້. ຄລິກໃສ່ໃບອ"
"ະນຸຍາດໃດໜຶ່ງເພື່ອຕິດຕາມລະຫັດໃບອະນຸຍາດ\n"
"            ຂອງລູກຄ້າແຕ່ລະຄົນ."

#. module: software_reseller
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:software_reseller.welcome_article_body
